OL,3,CFourth arrest in grave tampering
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FPolice have arrested a fourth man as
OL,7,Fpart of an investigation into grave
OL,8,Ftampering in Rotherham.
OL,10,FThe 29-year-old was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,12,Fcriminal damage following an incident
OL,13,Fat at All Saints Church graveyard,
OL,14,FLaughton-en-le-Morthen.
OL,16,FHe has been bailed pending further
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
