OL,3,CFourth arrest in grave tampering
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FTwo men aged 25 and a 53-year-old man
OL,7,Fwho were arrested in February on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of causing a public nuisance
OL,9,Fand conspiracy to commit criminal
OL,10,Fdamage remain on bail.
OL,12,FPolice were called to the church on 1
OL,13,FFebruary following reports of an
OL,14,Fincident and officers remained on site
OL,15,Ffor eight days. The church yard was
OL,16,Fclosed to the public.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
