OL,3,CFourth arrest in grave tampering
OL,4,Cinvestigation
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the family
OL,7,Fof the deceased had been informed and
OL,8,Fwas being supported by specialist
OL,9,Fofficers. The force is continuing to
OL,10,Fappeal for information.
